{"type": "article", "id": 5777, "title": "SHARP 厨房组合", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-02T07:40:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233946uD8ol6VAG9vfEwyC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t现居住在纽约的波兰裔设计师 Daniel Libeskind 为意大利厨具品牌 Varenna Poliform 设计了一款名为「SHARP」的厨房组合。SHARP 系列与他之前的 Web 书柜及 SHARP 衣柜一样，充满棱角的设计，使用坚硬的大理石作为台面，很容易让人联想到他的建筑作品，功能与外形兼备，也颠覆了传统厨房的概念。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233945GKxYAkp0DVz5ubLI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233945Tkc8R1MoGBFKxdmJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.309375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233945RGSliYsT8bzEtMa3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}